---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import me from "../images/me.webp";
---

<section aria-labelledby="about" class="mt-36">
  <h2 id="about" class="font-syne text-3xl font-bold">About Me</h2>
  <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr]">
    <div>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        Hello! My name is David and I control my computer mostly using my voice.
        In early 2022 I started building a browser extension called <a
          href="https://rango.click"
          class="text-accent"
        >
          Rango
        </a>
        that allows users to navigate the web by voice. Watch <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QYkjgd6_s4o&t=305s"
          class="text-accent"
        >
          Salma Alam-Naylor talk to Kevin Powell</a
        > about how much Rango has helped her when she needed it.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
        I enjoy building all kinds of different things using web technologies.
        Here are some of the technologies a have been using recently:
        <ul class="skills-list mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 pl-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <li>HTML</li>
          <li>CSS</li>
          <li>Javascript</li>
          <li>TypeScript</li>
          <li>React</li>
          <li>Node.js</li>
          <li>Tailwind</li>
          <li>Jest</li>
          <li>Puppeteer</li>
          <li>Astro</li>
          <li>Next.js</li>
          <li>Python</li>
        </ul>
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4">
        I also enjoy learning languages. Apart from my native <strong
          >Spanish</strong
        >, I speak fluent <strong>English</strong>, conversational <strong
          >German</strong
        >
        and a bit of <strong>French</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="picture mx-auto aspect-square w-[min(300px,90%)] rounded-xl">
        <Image
          src={me}
          alt="A picture of me with my cat Shiro"
          width="200"
          height="200"
          class="mx-auto aspect-square w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .picture {
    position: relative;
    transition: translate 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }

  .picture:hover {
    translate: -5px -5px;
  }

  .picture:before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 40%;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }

  .picture:hover:before {
    opacity: 0%;
  }

  .picture:after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: -1;
    right: -10px;
    left: 10px;
    top: 10px;
    bottom: -10px;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    transition: translate 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }

  .picture:hover:after {
    translate: 10px 10px;
  }

  .skills-list li:before {
    content: "Â»";
    position: relative;
    top: -1px;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
